Description:
Contemporary Lines, Open Spaces
This superbly located townhouse features light-filled rooms and generous proportions over all three levels.
Master bedroom highlights include ensuite, WIR and large north-facing terrace. Mezzanine level incorporates bedrooms 2 and 3 (each with private balconies and BIRs), as well as study and central bathroom. Large open plan living area flows out to the private entertainers courtyard. Kitchen is equipped with black granite bench tops, double dishwasher and Blanco appliances. High security levels with intercom, remote gate access and OSP.
Other features include: separate laundry, downstairs powder room, reverse cycle air conditioning, polished timber floors and new carpets.
With immediate access to Smith and Brunswick Streets - and multiple transport options - all that's left to do is move in.

Sale by Set Date 17/9/2009
Urban professionals will love this exclusive, architect designed boutique inner city development. The properties showcase sparkling city views and trend setting finishes for a truly signature interior.
Comprising six, two bedroom apartments and two lavish penthouses you can revel in a low maintenance latte lifestyle, close to premier amenities.
Comprising gourmet Caesar Stone kitchens, spacious light filled living and dining areas breeze onto private courtyards or long balconies, two double bedrooms, designer bathrooms, security entry and car accommodation.
Enviously located, a stroll to cosmopolitan Smith Street shopping and Fitzroy Street Cafe precinct, tram transport and scenic parklands. Easy car access and close to handy freeway access and only minutes into the city. Offering huge first home owner's grants of up to $17,000 and $32,000. An opportunity not to be missed.

A Little Slice Of New York

Features exposed trusses and raw face brickwork and cleverly refurbished with nothing to spend. This creative use of space offers entrance hall, spacious living environment, unique upstairs bedroom, Superb bathroom, ideal study or small 2nd bedroom, outdoor terrace and BBQ area, laundry. Description:
HUGE STAMP DUTY SAVINGS!
From the eclectic fashion and art precinct in Gertrude Street to Smith Street's diversity and development, Collingwood has seen a return to near-city living.
Perfectly located in Collingwood within walking distance to the city and with transport at your doorstep, this new boutique development will comprise 30 stylish inner city apartments. One, two and two bedroom plus study apartments will be available.
Logical floorplans and spacious apartments appointed with quality fixtures all with large balconies. Also featuring security entry, secure underground carparking, heating/cooling and with storage cages available.
8 Stanley Street is positioned to facilitate near-city convenience. Although secure off-street parking is provided, quality shopping and the cafe culture of Smith and Brunswick Streets are close at hand. Melbourne's famous MCG and other sports arena's are within easy reach, as are the major city hospitals, restaurants, and all the entertainment facilities of Melbourne city itself. The Fitzroy and Exhibition Gardens are your backyard.
More details available at www.8stanleystreet.com or call Caine Real Estate today on 8413 8088.

Description:
SUBLIMELY SUCCESSFUL WAREHOUSE CONVERSION
A conversion that reveals distinctive designer flair and fabulous attention to detail has created a light-filled contemporary residence of huge appeal framed by former factory lines that ensure total privacy.
Enhanced by preferred northerly aspects, complemented by convenient double garage, this superb modern home casts a discreet impression from the outside before revealing spectacular spaces within.
Huge living/dining areas have their already impressive dimensions enhanced by soaring double ceilings and an accompanying courtyard that cleverly fulfils an additional role as an effective atrium.
The sublime upstairs main bedroom features a sunny terrace overlooking the elegant courtyard and is further complemented by walk-in robes and a lavish en suite.
Second upstairs bedroom, third downstairs and second bathroom provide outstanding accommodation.
Great granite and smeg kitchen with walk-in pantry and cafe windows onto the courtyard caters with elegant efficiency and completes a stunning set of inner city spaces.
Ample storage, reverse cycle heating/cooling, gas fire place, intercom entry and video security put fine finishing touches to the ideal example of property that has evolved 'from factory to fabulous'!
